      strong description:
      light  A concept for redefining the “pay-to-cut” model of skipping past long lines. KarmaQ attempts to introduce a “contribute-to-cut” model to allow people to earn the right to skip lines by contributing to society.

  section.section
    h2.header_3 Context
    
  section.section
    p.par This was a Graduate Studio assignment where we were given the task of coming up with a concept to present in a photo essay. We picked a aspect of Hong Kong contemporary Hong Kong culture and chose to study it. We were interested in how we could change the perception of “queuing” up in Hong Kong.
    
