    h2.header_2 Concepts
    
  section.section
    h2.header_3 Design Goal
    
  section.section
    p.par We aim to redistribute the time spent waiting in line to time spent doing social good such as charity work; provide an incentive to do social good and prioritise people who do social good. As the line is a reflection of our social values, we hope to redesign the line and use it as an instrument to influence society.
    
  section.section
